        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Symbolic Analysis [S+N]\n\nBefore plotting, Maxima can derive exact analytic properties of a surface.\nHere we take the saddle surface and compute its gradient and Hessian\nsymbolically, classifying the critical point at the origin.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Define the surface symbolically */\nf(x, y) := x^2 - y^2$\nf(x, y);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 125,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "x^2-y^2"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 125,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Gradient: nabla f */\ngrad_f : [diff(f(x,y), x), diff(f(x,y), y)];",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 126,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "\\left[ 2\\,x , -\\left(2\\,y\\right) \\right] "
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 126,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Hessian matrix */\nH : matrix(\n  [diff(f(x,y), x, 2), diff(f(x,y), x, 1, y, 1)],\n  [diff(f(x,y), y, 1, x, 1), diff(f(x,y), y, 2)]\n);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 127,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "\\ifx\\endpmatrix\\undefined\\pmatrix{\\else\\begin{pmatrix}\\fi 2&0\\cr 0&-2\\cr\\ifx\\endpmatrix\\undefined}\\else\\end{pmatrix}\\fi "
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 127,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Determinant of the Hessian classifies the critical point.\n   det < 0 => saddle point at the origin. */\ndet_H : determinant(H);",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 128,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "data": {
            "text/latex": [
              "-4"
            ]
          },
          "execution_count": 128,
          "metadata": {},
          "output_type": "execute_result"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "The Hessian determinant is negative, confirming the origin is a **saddle\npoint** — exactly what we see in the 3D plot above.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## Trigonometric Surfaces\n\nPeriodic surfaces built from sine and cosine, producing wave-like\ngeometries.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
